<plot>Bob Blake is on his way home for Christmas aboard a train. When Bob inadvertently misses his stop, he ends up stuck for Christmas with a number of other salesmen in the hamlet of Grand Crossing. There he finds romance with the local telegraph girl, Beth Elliott. Bob becomes entangled with her fight to keep her property from a greedy co-opter.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?596852</url></doc>
